46. Write a Java program to display the system time.

System.currentTimeMillis()
- Display System Time

%tc
- Display complete time and date information

%n
outputs a line break
outputs the correct platform-specific line separator, it is portable across platforms

===

import java.io.Console;
import java.io.File;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class w3 {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.format("\nCurrent Date time: %tc%n\n",System.currentTimeMillis());#
        
    }
}

>>
Current Date time: Tue Nov 08 06:43:44 MYT 2022
